{"tid":1631582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［總結左小小］　要嬴依埸運動 請大家花兩分鍾入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:59:32.000Z","uid":11374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac989e0ce6f2d532d7f7c792143b8d768b7ce79c","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"第一.  善用不推文回覆<br />\n我見到好多分化POST 你知我知單眼佬都知  但就仲係有好多巴絲 一味屌 但唔用不推文回覆<br />\n<br />\n第二. 堅持五大訴求<br />\n解散警隊個個都想 但五大訴求 由運動初期用到依家<br />\n文宣去到國際性都係講緊爭取五大訴求<br />\n要訴求既事太多 但請唔好亂改我地個中心 &quot;五大訴求 缺一不可&quot;<br />\n10點鳩叫唔知邊隻鬼話轉9點 情況係點大家睇得到<br />\n<br />\n第三. Be Humble<br />\n講過好多次 曾經有好轉 但最近大家必須不斷提醒自己<br />\nEG. 影相既 好聲好氣講 而唔係大叫&quot;咪撚影相呀BLABLABLA&quot;<br />\n<br />\n第四. 鶳 目的<br />\n在於黑警執法不公 示威者被打會反被拘捕<br />\n我地為求自保 公義 先進行鶳<br />\n鶳原則建議: <span style=\"color: red;\">對方先動手或手持攻擊性武器</span><br />\n一般言論不同 請大家不必多加理會 無視便可<br />\n我地唔係紅衛兵 <br />\n面對準政權 我地依然係雞蛋既一群  <br />\n<br />\n第五. 裝修選址要適當<br />\n立埸不同 可選擇罷買<br />\n個人建議: <span style=\"color: red;\">但凡 政治白色恐怖 / 黑社會 / 督灰陷害手足被捕之商店 可考慮幫其裝修</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第六. 明白何為割席<br />\n五毛進化左 佢地想推示威者極端化<br />\n但凡有意見 就會立即以 割席 為由 不容大家討論以作改善<br />\n大家要記住 運動至今 係因為不斷進步改善 而走到依家<br />\n提出意見不代表割席<br />\n<br />\n我願與手足站在同一陣線<br />\n共同承擔</span>"},{"pid":"485b0f9284fa857830afc0c3930aeac691358cba","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"8f57d7ca2a179dcd7747bb5c7695beb948d3642c","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"7702414eb288eefdf192ce4897a7ca33cb7ceebb","tid":1631582,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84be1fe607c5b7fd30778073b9dcf2441751cb99","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"6c67414e70182245b7f2da5b947331b63f9975e9","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"3e7a8719fb656ff2f5d4666d8f70df3640f1881c","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"3a0a3954672c4c65ff1c8ce2724f77bd54362c21","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ba1c9dcff31dbc81bbd2b3f01f815dd1a76329","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff222bd54920b85a6dba57fceccd7dd6c4981b76","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d236d8808258288e4f0bd79ba940e7e5c10e419","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理"},{"pid":"334fee7f07f829b43308dfc9eff1f43d1d466fb5","tid":1631582,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:40:40.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"5f2a12b542f93608b0793f7a13dd70c2887bebe1","tid":1631582,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"講左好耐 五毛會開極大量分化po<br />\n<br />\n自己同自己嘈 引大家無限討論<br />\n<br